'''phenomenology'''
# A [[philosophy]] based on the [[intuitive]] [[experience]] of [[phenomena]], and on the [[premise]] that [[reality]] consists of [[object]]s and [[event]]s as [[consciously]] [[perceived]] by [[conscious being]]s
# A [[movement]] based on this, originated about 1905 by Edmund Husserl.

